mixin cards(img, postTitle)
        article(class="col s12 m6 l4")
            div(class="card")
                div(class="card-image waves-effect waves-block waves-light")
                    img(class="activator" src="../assets/images/"+img alt="")
                div(class="card-content")
                    span(class="card-title grey-text activator text-darken-4")=postTitle
                        i(class="material-icons right") more_vert
                div(class="card-reveal")
                    span(class="card-title grey-text activator text-darken-4")
                        i(class="material-icons right") close
                    p Here is some more information about this product that is only revealed once clicked on.
